## Important Notes

1. **In-Memory Data**: All operational data is lost on server restart
2. **SQLite**: Only user data (accounts, states) is persisted
3. **SSE**: Single connection per client, sends snapshots on connect
4. **Development Mode**: Authentication bypassed when DEVELOPMENT_MODE is set
5. **Round-Robin**: Fleet assignment uses round-robin for even distribution
6. **No-Go Zones**: All movement types respect no-go zones
7. **Water Areas**: Naval units can only exist on water areas